The,Canadian,Sales,Tax,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,sales,tax,information,with,their,applications,by,using,the,postal,abbreviations,of,Canada,The,following,methods,are,available,Get,the,current,GST,global,sales,tax,Get,the,current,HST,harmonized,sales,tax,for,a,province,Get,the,current,HST,for,all,provinces,Get,the,current,GST,for,a,province,Get,the,current,PST,provincial,sales,tax,for,all,provinces,Get,the,total,applicable,tax,for,a,province,and,Get,the,total,applicable,tax,for,all,provinces,Currently,this,API,supports,JSON,for,responses